snippet.title: Capcom Fighting Collection 2 – Announcement Trailer – Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
This will be a collection to remember! Capcom Fighting Collection 2 on Nintendo Switch includes 8 fighting games from across Capcom's history and will release in 2025.
 
Capcom vs. SNK: Millennium Fight 2000 Pro
Capcom vs. SNK 2: Mark of the Millennium 2001
Capcom Fighting Evolution
Street Fighter Alpha 3 UPPER
Project Justice
Power Stone
Power Stone 2
Plasma Sword: Nightmare of Bilstein
 
#CapcomFightingCollection2 #NintendoDirect #NintendoSwitch

Visit Nintendo.com for more info: https://www.nintendo.com/us/
